\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：而家條女就係坐巴士識返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01aa249794a836d695c48e0bb5ce3b30372b567c","tid":258601,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:29:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識坐一定坐逆行車方向同貼窗口既位，有時可以靠玻璃既全內反射昅女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw樓主架巴士路線一定係成日經街市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n教下你啦，有時見到啲呀嬸肥婆上車就記住要放定隻腳係對面登底，扮唔比人坐。<br />\n你有2隻腳，啱啱好可以封印晒對面2個位，跟住到果啲中學生上車既站啲女上車果時，而佢地又行到埋黎果時，你即刻縮返埋對腳，動作誇張啲，佢就會下意識地坐係你隔離，咁就可以輕鬆可以昅成程女女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：而家條女就係坐巴士識返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比我見到條友lon完腳我都唔坐啦，仲話要誇張d縮比佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52db6b6408ce924cc346f4bbfcf608860d0893bf","tid":258601,"uid":44487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:43:04.000Z","msg":"你都好呀<br />\n我坐親都係3位老漢圍住"},{"pid":"2469687b87d3165c4acb8b7b1eac4668af1ff528","tid":258601,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:44:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都好呀<br />\n我坐親都係3位老漢圍住</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27b08713658c57888c0bb9953bfe3224ae8499b","tid":258601,"uid":91664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T12:03:27.000Z","msg":"當你坐上層，就會有靚女坐下層架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8bc30f4f61fe39504044f948e7bc22c9c59598","tid":258601,"uid":117855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score